    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>About Rise of Elements</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Rise of Elements</i>, you will play as one of the Champions of Aetheron, tasked with restoring balance to a cosmos disrupted by the mysterious Void. Armed with your Champion’s unique abilities, harness the powers of air, earth, fire, water, and void to engage in strategic battles across the realm. Gather elemental shards to fuel your Champion’s power, and realize your full potential by achieving elemental combat mastery. Emerge victorious in Argos’s Tournament of Champions to restore balance to the world of Aetheron and triumph over the Void’s untethered chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/ec2992c6dbc8831fe08bf7a2a4806dad.poster.avif?t=1742511436\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/ec2992c6dbc8831fe08bf7a2a4806dad.webm?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/ec2992c6dbc8831fe08bf7a2a4806dad.mp4?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Tactical Match-3 Combat</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use match effect gemstones to unleash powerful elemental attacks on your opponent. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rise of Elements follows a Match-3 gameplay structure, with each gem representing an element: Air, Earth, Fire, Water, and Void. Each element possesses unique attributes that trigger effects when like elements are matched. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Match three or more gems of the same element to charge your Champion's abilities. Matching 4 or more gems creates special gems that change the way you play, like bombs, amplifier gems and power gems. Out-Match your rivals and achieve victory in head-to-head combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/049bebfb8d49d957c116892168f458de.poster.avif?t=1742511436\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/049bebfb8d49d957c116892168f458de.webm?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/049bebfb8d49d957c116892168f458de.mp4?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Casually or Competitively with Different Game Modes</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take your time in Moves Mode, or engage in a hardcore test of skill in Timed Mode, a fast-paced, more competitive take on the core Rise of Elements experience. With multiple ways to play, choose the Mode that best suits your needs and skill level!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/25d2a7a1253efdd07bf9ddd8a237e31e.poster.avif?t=1742511436\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/25d2a7a1253efdd07bf9ddd8a237e31e.webm?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/25d2a7a1253efdd07bf9ddd8a237e31e.mp4?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choose Your Champion </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Select one of the Champions of Aetheron and take on opponents in one-on-one battles, harnessing their unique elemental abilities and skill sets. Each Champion has their own style, story, and motivations to master and discover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/61659a4ddcb868e35a2efbb2fe5a0a1a.poster.avif?t=1742511436\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/61659a4ddcb868e35a2efbb2fe5a0a1a.webm?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/61659a4ddcb868e35a2efbb2fe5a0a1a.mp4?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover the Story of Aetheron</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in the epic world of Aetheron, where elemental power reigns supreme.  Uncover the secrets of Aetheron, its Champions, and even Argos himself in exciting PvE narrative adventures.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/c238003383d0aa2f6cbeecbe5e6cfdb7.poster.avif?t=1742511436\" width=800 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/c238003383d0aa2f6cbeecbe5e6cfdb7.webm?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3170850/extras/c238003383d0aa2f6cbeecbe5e6cfdb7.mp4?t=1742511436\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to fight for Aetheron? Emerge victorious from Argos’s Tournament, and seize your destiny as the reigning Champion of the Elements!</p>",
